### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:53128
@accessToken = 12345
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check - No Auth Required
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


### Bridge Request - Default Caching (single_usage parameter omitted - defaults to false)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bridge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "serverPath": "npx",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "args": [
    "-y",
    "@upstash/context7-mcp"
  ],
  "params": {},
  "env": {},
  "single_usage": true
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/bridge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "serverPath": "uvx",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "args": [
    "mcp-server-time"
  ],
  "params": {}
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/bridge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "serverPath": "npx",
    "args": [
        "-y",
        "@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem",
        "/tmp"],
    "method": "tools/list",
    "params": {}
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/bridge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "serverPath": "npx",
    "args": [
        "-y",
        "@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem",
        "/home/codemie"],
    "method": "tools/call",
    "params": {
      "name": "list_directory",
      "arguments": {
        "path": "/home/codemie"
      }
    }
}


### Bridge Request - Streamable-http
POST {{baseUrl}}/bridge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "serverPath": "http://127.0.0.1:3001/mcp",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "args": [],
  "params": {},
  "env": {},
  "auth_token": null,
  "http_transport_type": "streamable-http"
}

### Bridge Request - Connection Error (demonstrates enhanced error details)
# This request will fail with ECONNREFUSED and return detailed error information
POST {{baseUrl}}/bridge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "serverPath": "http://127.0.0.1:9999/mcp",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "args": [],
  "params": {},
  "http_transport_type": "streamable-http"
}
### Tool calls
POST {{baseUrl}}/bridge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "serverPath": "http://127.0.0.1:3001/mcp",
  "method": "tools/call",
  "args": [],
  "params": {"name": "echo", "arguments": {"message": "hello"}},
  "env": {},
  "auth_token": null,
  "http_transport_type": "streamable-http"
}

